verbose_text: The strong upregulation of full-length (P) RR protein expression in HeLa cells cultivated in high glucose conditions observed in this study is consistent with previous studies which demonstrated an upregulation of (P) RR mRNA and protein in hearts as well as kidneys of diabetic rats, of (P) RR protein in kidneys of patients with diabetic nephropathy, and of (P) RR mRNA and protein in rat mesangial cells by glucose.
